 Fl\u00f8y\n}}\n----\n{{footballbox\n|date = 12 November 2008\n|time = 19:00 [[Central European Time|CET]]\n|team1 = [[Aalesunds FK|Aalesund]]\n|score = 3\u20131\n|report = [https://www.nifs.no/kampfakta.php?kamp_id=336970&land=1&t=64&u=3666&lag1=46&lag2=10 Report]\n|team2 = [[Sogndal Fotball|Sogndal]]\n|goals1 = [[Tor Hogne Aar\u00f8y|Aar\u00f8y]] {{goal|14||31||43}}\n|goals2 = [[H\u00e5vard Flo]] {{goal|43}}\n|stadium = [[Color Line Stadion]], [[\u00c5lesund]]\n|attendance = 8,646\n|referee = [[Terje Hauge]], Olsvik\n}}\n\n''Aalesund won 7\u20132 on aggregate and remained in [[2009 Tippeligaen|Tippeligaen]].''\n\n==Top goal scorers==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Rank\n!Scorer\n!Club\n!Goals\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|1\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[P\u00e9ter Kov\u00e1cs (footballer)|Peter Kovacs]]\n|[[Odd Grenland]] \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|22\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|2\n|{{flagicon|Norway}} Kenneth Kvalheim\n|[[Moss FK|Moss]] \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|21\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|3\n|{{flagicon|Norway}} [[Morten Fevang]]\n|[[Odd Grenland]] \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|15\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|4\n|{{flagicon|Jamaica}} [[Fabian Taylor]]\n|[[Notodden FK|Notodden]] \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|14\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=3|5\n|{{flagicon|Norway}} Vegard Braaten\n|[[Alta IF|Alta]] \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|13\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Norway}} [[Martin Wiig]]\n|[[Sarpsborg Sparta FK|Sarpsborg Sparta]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|13 \n|-\n|{{flagicon|Norway}} Lars Lafton\n|[[H\u00f8nefoss BK|H\u00f8nefoss]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|13\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|8\n|{{flagicon|Denmark}} [[Allan Borgvardt]]\n|[[Bryne FK|Bryne]] \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|12\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|9\n|{{flagicon|Norway}} [[Geir Ludvig Fevang]]\n|[[IK Start|Start]] \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|11\n|-\n|}\n\n<small>Source: [http://fotball.vg.no/bors/toppscorern.php?sesong_id=423 VG Nett]{{Dead link|date=September 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</small>\n\n==Relegated teams==\nThese three teams were relegated from the Tippeligaen in 2007:\n\n*[[Odd Grenland]]\n*[[IK Start|Start]]\n*[[Sandefjord Fotball|Sandefjord]]\n\n==Promoted teams==\nThese four teams were promoted from the 2. divisjon in 2007:\n\n*[[Alta IF|Alta]]\n*[[IL H\u00f8dd|H\u00f8dd]]\n*[[Nybergsund IL-Trysil|Nybergsund-Trysil]]\n*[[Sandnes Ulf]]\n\n== See also ==\n* [[2008 Tippeligaen]]\n* [[2008 2. divisjon]]\n* [[2008 3. divisjon]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* 1. divisjon 2008 on NRK Sport: <span class=\"plainlinks\">[http://www.nrksport.no/fotball/1_divisjon/?arr=l39&sesong=2008&type=terminliste Fixtures and results] - [http://www.nrksport.no/fotball/1_divisjon/?arr=l39&sesong=2008&type=lister Top scorers, Yellow cards, Red cards] - [http://www.nrksport.no/fotball/1_divisjon/?arr=l39&sesong=2008&type=tabeller Standings]</span>\n\n{{1. divisjon}}\n{{2008 in Norwegian football}}\n\n[[Category:1. divisjon seasons]]\n[[Category:2008 in Norwegian football|2]]\n[[Category:2008\u201309 in European second tier association football leagues|Norway]]\n[[Category:2007\u201308 in European second tier association football leagues|Norway]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football league season\n| competition        = 1. divisjon\n| season             = 2008\n| winners            = [[Odd Grenland]]\n| promoted           = Odd Grenland<br>[[Sandefjord Fotball|Sandefjord]]<br>[[IK Start|Start]]\n| relegated          = [[Sandnes Ulf]]<br />[[IL H\u00f8dd|H\u00f8dd]]\n| continentalcup1    = \n| continentalcup1 qualifiers = \n| continentalcup2    = \n| continentalcup2 qualifiers = \n| matches            = 240\n| total goals        = 762\n| league topscorer   = [[P\u00e9ter Kov\u00e1cs (footballer)|P\u00e9ter Kov\u00e1cs]]<br>(22 goals)\n| biggest home win   = \n| biggest away win   = \n| highest scoring    = \n<!--\nPLEASE USE THESE PARAMETERS ONLY IF THERE