59|24|47|N|5|16|46|E|region:NO}}}}\n{{Location map~| Norway South| label=[[KIL Toppfotball|Kongsvinger]]| position=top | coordinates = {{coord|60|11|42|N|11|59|15|E|region:NO}}}}\n{{Location map~| Norway South| label=[[Moss FK|Moss]] | position=right | coordinates = {{coord|59|27|33|N|10|42|3|E|region:NO}}}}\n{{Location map~| Norway South| label=[[Sandnes Ulf|Sandnes&nbsp;Ulf]]| position=right| coordinates = {{coord|58|51|34|N|5|43|33|E|region:NO}}}}\n{{Location map~| Norway South| label=[[Notodden FK|Notodden ]]| position=left| coordinates = {{coord|59|34|13|N|9|16|16|E|region:NO}} }}\n{{Location map~| Norway South| label=[[Sandefjord Fotball|Sandefjord]] | position=bottom | coordinates = {{coord|59|8|14|N|10|10|46|E|region:NO}}}}\n{{Location map~| Norway South| label=[[IL H\u00f8dd|H\u00f8dd]] | position=right| coordinates = {{coord|62|20|23|N|5|52|54|E|region:NO}}}}\n}}\nThe '''2008 [[1. divisjon]]''' season (referred to as '''[[Adecco]]ligaen''' for sponsorship reasons) began on 5 April 2008 and ended on 1 November 2008.<ref>{{cite web | title = 1. divisjon - Fixtures 2008 | work=NRK Sport | url=http://www.nrksport.no/fotball/1_divisjon/?arr=l39&sesong=2008&type=terminliste | accessdate=2008-03-20}}</ref>\n\nIn 2009, the number of teams in the top tier, [[Eliteserien|Tippeligaen]], will expand from fourteen to sixteen.<ref>{{cite web|title=Tippeligaen utvides til 16 lag |work=Football Association of Norway |url=http://www.fotball.no/table.asp?p=53184&cat=51834&x=1&a=221127 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20080804140606/http://www.fotball.no/table.asp?p=53184&cat=51834&x=1&a=221127 |url-status=dead |archive-date=2008-08-04 |accessdate=2008-03-20 |date=2008-03-08 |language=Norwegian }}</ref> Therefore, 2008 was a transitional season, in which more teams were promoted to the top flight, and less teams relegated to the [[2. divisjon]], than usual. Automatic promotion was awarded to the teams finishing in the top three places in the standings. Only the two teams at the bottom of the standings were relegated to the 2. divisjon, as opposed to the regular four.\n\nThe three clubs relegated from the Tippeligaen in [[2007 Tippeligaen|2007]] were [[Odd Grenland]], [[IK Start|Start]] and [[Sandefjord Fotball|Sandefjord]]. At the conclusion of the season, all three had managed to secure promotion, with Odd Grenland being confirmed as champions of the 1. divisjon after defeating Start 3\u20132 in the penultimate round.<ref>{{cite web | title=Odd ble serievinnere | work=Adresseavisen | url=http://fotball.adressa.no/forstediv/article121033.ece | accessdate=2008-11-04 | date=2008-10-25 | language=Norwegian | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023233805/http://fotball.adressa.no/forstediv/article121033.ece | archive-date=2012-10-23 | url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n[[Sandnes Ulf]] and [[IL H\u00f8dd|H\u00f8dd]] were relegated to the 2. divisjon after finishing in fifteenth and sixteenth place respectively. It was Sandnes Ulf's first season at the second level since 1972. [[Nybergsund IL|Nybergsund]], who had never previously played at the second level, retained their spot, finishing in eighth place.\n\nAs in previous years, there was a two-legged promotion playoff at the end of the season, this time between the fourth-placed team in the 1. divisjon ([[Sogndal Fotball|Sogndal]]) and the thirteenth-placed team in the Tippeligaen ([[Aalesunds FK|Aalesund]]). Aalesund kept their spot in the Tippeligaen, beating Sogndal 4-1 away, 3-1 at home, and 7-2 on aggregate.<ref>{{cite web | title = Beramming kvalikkamper til Tippeligaen | work=Football Association of Norway | url=http://www.fotball.no/t1.aspx?p=51831&x=1&a=237665 | accessdate=2008-11-04| date=2008-11-03 | language=Norwegian}}</ref>\n\n==League table==\n<onlyinclude>{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=PR\n\n|team1=ODD|name_ODD=[[Odd Grenland]]\n|team2=SF|name_SF=[[Sandefjord Fotball|Sandefjord]]\n|team3=STA|name_STA=[[IK Start|Start]]\n|team4=SIL|name_SIL=[[Sogndal Fotball|Sogndal]]\n|team5=H\u00d8N|name_H\u00d8N=[[H\u00f8nefoss BK]]\n|team6=NOT|name_NOT=[[Notodden FK|Notodden]]\n|team7=HAU|name_HAU=[[FK Haugesund|Haugesund]]\n|team8=NIL|name_NIL=[[Nybergsund IL-Trysil|Nybergsund-Trysil]]\n|team9=MFK|name_MFK=[[Moss FK|Moss]]\n|team10=SSFK|name_SSFK=[[FK Sparta Sarpsborg|Sarpsborg Sparta]]\n|team11=BRY|name_BRY=[[Bryne FK|Bryne]]\n|team12=L\u00d8V|name_L\u00d8V=[[L\u00f8v-Ham Fotball|L\u00f8v-Ham]]\n|team13=KIL|name_KIL=[[Kongsvinger IL Toppfotball|Kongsvinger]]\n|team14=ALT|name_ALT=[[Alta IF|Alta]]\n|team15=ULF|name_ULF=[[Sandnes Ulf]]\n|team16=ILH|name_ILH=[[IL H\u00f8dd|H\u00f8dd]]\n\n|win_ODD=20|draw_ODD=5|loss_ODD=5|gf_ODD=76|ga_ODD=44|status_ODD=CP\n|win_SF=17|draw_SF=9|loss_SF=4|gf_SF=46|ga_SF=25|status_SF=P\n|win_STA=17|draw_STA=8|loss_STA=5|gf_STA=58|ga_STA=34|status_STA=P\n|win_SIL=15|draw_SIL=9|loss_SIL=6|gf_SIL=53|ga_SIL=36\n|win_H\u00d8N=15|draw_H\u00d8N=6|loss_H\u00d8N=9|gf_H\u00d8N=47|ga_H\u00d8N=33\n|win_NOT=12|draw_NOT=10|loss_NOT=8|gf_NOT=55|ga_NOT=40\n|win_HAU=11|draw_HAU=9|loss_HAU=10|gf_HAU=48|ga_HAU=47\n|win_NIL=12|draw_NIL=6|loss_NIL=12|gf_NIL=49|ga_NIL=53\n|win_MFK=9|draw_MFK=12|loss_MFK=9|gf_MFK=63|ga_MFK=54\n|win_SSFK=10|draw_SSFK=7|loss_SSFK=13|gf_SSFK=45|ga_SSFK=43\n|win_BRY=10|draw_BRY=6|loss_BRY=14|gf_BRY=38|ga_BRY=53\n|win_L\u00d8V=9|draw_L\u00d8V=7|loss_L\u00d8V=14|gf_L\u00d8V=37|ga_L\u00d8V=45\n|win_KIL=8|draw_KIL=6|loss_KIL=16|gf_KIL=33|ga_KIL=58\n|win_ALT=8|draw_ALT=2|loss_ALT=20|gf_ALT=49|ga_ALT=66\n|win_ULF=5|draw_ULF=10|loss_ULF=15|gf_ULF=36|ga_ULF=55|status_ULF=R\n|win_ILH=2|draw_ILH=8|loss_ILH=20|gf_ILH=29|ga_ILH=76|status_ILH=R\n\n|col_P=green1|text_P=Promotion to [[2009 Tippeligaen|Tippeligaen]]\n|result1=P|result2=P|result3=P\n|col_PP=green3|text_PP=Qualification for the [[2008 1. divisjon#Promotion play-offs|promotion play-offs]]\n|result4=PP\n|col_R=red1|text_R=Relegation to [[2009 2. divisjon|2. divisjon]]\n|result15=R|result16=R\n\n|class_rules=1) points; 2) goal difference; 3) 